::Spears::

Her trainer side still active, she looked at Firearm,"I understand. 
But I feel fine, I feel like a new bot infact. I don't really want to 
go into stasis.  I hardly know what happened after they got me."  She 
looked down and sighed. "I just wish I knew what happened to Striker. 
I...I feel responcable in some way."  Her head lowered another inch 
and she looked like her spark was breaking.    

her trainer side wanted to see inside of the CF and learn all she 
could, then give the info to Prebon.
